        },
        "type": "text",
        "version": 1,
        "inline_content": [
          {
            "Text": "If you write Windows software, you need to provide an installer. Almost all installers are created by a tool (e.g. "
          },
          {
            "Text": "WiX",
            "Link": "http://wix.sourceforge.net/"
          },
          {
            "Text": ", "
