            [
              "NSIS",
              [
                [
                  "a",
                  "http://nsis.sourceforge.net/"
                ]
              ]
            ],
            [
              " was my weapon of choice: it’s free, (relatively) easy to learn, (relatively well) documented and since other people used it, there are examples to learn from."
            ]
          ]
        },
        "type": "text",
        "version": 1,
        "inline_content": [
          {
            "Text": "As everyone else, I did my installers with a tool. "
          },
          {
            "Text": "NSIS",
            "Link": "http://nsis.sourceforge.net/"
          },
          {
            "Text": " was my weapon of choice: it’s free, (relatively) easy to learn, (relatively well) documented and since other people used it, there are examples to learn from."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "alive": true,
        "created_by": "bb760e2d-d679-4b64-b2a9-03005b21870a",
        "created_time": 1531736996113,
        "id": "14111b8b-1d75-40d2-9ef5-5f1966c9103d",
